steps.name: Authorize user with valid email admin@gmail.com and password admin
Click on guest dropdown
Click on `Увійти` button
Set values 'admin@gmail.com'/'admin' for `Емейл` and `Пароль` fields
Fill in Password field: 'admin'
Click on Submit button
Click on dropdown for authorized user in top right corner of header
Click on 'Мій профіль' button in dropdown for authorized users
Click on 'Додати' button
Click on 'Додати гурток' button
Fill 'Назва' field with Name of club
Check off 'Спортивні секції' check-box from 'Категорія' group box
Enter 2 into the first age input and 16 in second age input
Click on 'Наступний крок' button
Enter gfhdfghfg data into Facebook field of 'Контакти' area
Enter fhfdhgfd@gmail.com data into Email field of 'Контакти' area
Enter ghdfghf data into WhatsApp field of 'Контакти' area
Enter grsgr data into Site field of 'Контакти' area
Enter efaefs data into Skype field of 'Контакти' area
Enter 7557565755 data into Phone number field of 'Контакти' area
Click on 'Наступний крок' button
Fill 'Опис' field with sfadsfadsfasdfasdfasfsdfadfasdffefewfwefwfЫ
Get error message
